  <p>BingoPlus turned its anniversary into a milestone disclosure. The DigiPlus Interactive-owned online bingo platform reported PHP 2.25 trillion in cumulative payouts to verified Filipino users as of December 31, 2025, the headline figure at its 2026 anniversary event held in a Pasay City ballroom on May 19.</p>

  <p>The number lands at a moment when DigiPlus is making the case to investors and to PAGCOR that its core domestic platforms have moved past the disruption of the third-quarter 2025 e-wallet delinking and are returning to a growth-and-scale narrative built on a stable, verified, large-volume user base.</p>

